  <brief_title>Effects of Lifestyle Modification on Metabolic Parameters in Type 2 Diabetic Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Lifestyle Modification Focusing on Exercise Intervention on Risk of Atherosclerosis and Metabolic Parameters in Type 2 Diabetic Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
